com.sitewhere.spi.device.event.processor

Interface IInboundEventProcessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ILifecycleComponent, ITenantLifecycleComponent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IInboundEventProcessorChain

    public interface IInboundEventProcessor
extends ITenantLifecycleComponent
    Allows interested entities to interact with SiteWhere inbound event processing.
